title: The Company Of  Wolves
description:
Description: Based upon The Bloody Chamber by Angela Carter, who also wrote the screenplay with director Neil Jordan.


This is a coming of age Fantasy-Horror using the traditional story of Red Riding Hood is explored for its sexual connotations.

This Film stars Sarah Patterson as Rosaleen and Angela Lansbury as Granny with David Warner and Brain Glover. Look out for Terrence Stamp in a cameo.
